value.name: 加山雄三 最後のフェス出演とTHE King ALL STARS、そして蘇る新世界
value.original_name: 加山雄三 最後のフェス出演とTHE King ALL STARS、そして蘇る新世界
value.overview: The program will also include live footage of THE KING ALL STARS' past live performances and the legendary "Yuzo Kayama's New World" event that was broadcast from Zushi Marina in 2020 with the participation of the band's splendid members and no audience. The digest of "Yuzo Kayama's New World" will also be broadcast!
